STATE of North Carolina
v.
Rex Dean PENLAND. No. 139A94-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2006. Kenneth J. Rose, Durham, Stephen G. Royster, Mount Airy, for Rex Dean Penland. Barry S. McNeill, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Ricky Bowman, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by the Attorney General on the 3rd day of March 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Stokes County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th day of May 2006."
